	(29032, 48, 0, 'There... There\'s no more time for me. I\'m done for. Finish me off, $N. Do it or they\'ll kill us both. $N... Remember Teldrassil, our beloved home. This world is worth saving.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_TIME_7'),
