	(29072, 22, 0, 'You don\'t remember me, do you? Blasted Scourge...They\'ve tried to drain of everything that made you a righteous force of reckoning. Every last ounce of good...Everything that made you a human!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_NOREM_5'),
	(29072, 23, 0, 'You don\'t remember me? When you were a child your mother would leave you in my care while she served at the Temple of the Moon. I held you in my arms and fed you with honey and sheep\'s milk to calm you until she would return. You were my little angel. Blasted Scourge... What have they done to you, $N?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_NOREM_6'),
