	(29173, 30, 0, 'Save your breath, old man. It might be the last you ever draw.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14700, 'Highlord Darion Mograine'),
	(29227, 31, 0, 'My son! My dear, beautiful boy!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14493, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
	(29173, 32, 0, 'Father!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14701, 'Highlord Darion Mograine'),
	(29173, 33, 0, 'Argh...what...is...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14702, 'Highlord Darion Mograine'),
	(29228, 34, 0, 'Father, you have returned!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14703, 'Darion Mograine'),
	(29228, 35, 0, 'You have been gone a long time, father. I thought...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14704, 'Darion Mograine'),
	(29227, 36, 0, 'Nothing could have kept me away from here, Darion. Not from my home and family.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14494, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
	(29228, 37, 0, 'Father, I wish to join you in the war against the undead. I want to fight! I can sit idle no longer!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14705, 'Darion Mograine'),
	(29227, 38, 0, 'Darion Mograine, you are barely of age to hold a sword, let alone battle the undead hordes of Lordaeron! I couldn\'t bear losing you. Even the thought...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14495, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
	(29228, 39, 0, 'If I die, father, I would rather it be on my feet, standing in defiance against the undead legions! If I die, father, I die with you!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14706, 'Darion Mograine'),
	(29227, 40, 0, 'My son, there will come a day when you will command the Ashbringer and, with it, mete justice across this land. I have no doubt that when that day finally comes, you will bring pride to our people and that Lordaeron will be a better place because of you. But, my son, that day is not today.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14496, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
	(29227, 41, 0, 'Do not forget...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14497, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
	(29183, 42, 0, 'Touching...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14803, 'The Lich King'),
	(29173, 43, 0, 'You have\'ve betrayed me! You betrayed us all you monster! Face the might of Mograine!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14707, 'Highlord Darion Mograine'),
	(29183, 44, 0, 'He\'s mine now...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14805, 'The Lich King'),
